description: Also known as Kujaku-hime Kada (Peacock Princess Kada) is 1 of the 4 Devas of the Kabuki District. A skilled professional gambler herself, she operates most of the gambling outfits in Kabuki District. In Chapter 305, she was revealed to be a member of the http://anidb.net/ch16863 [Harusame].
name: Kada
